Update blogs -> Upload (.png, .jpg)[Multiple], Form (Name, Description) -> Blob, Supa
Update Works -> Upload (.png, .jpg), Form (Name, Description) -> Blob, Supa
Update Bio   -> Form (Description)                            -> Supa
Update pfp   -> Upload (.png, .jpg)                           -> Blob


Data Structure:-

* Blob :

DB:
|- pfp.png
|- works
| |- zoey.png
| |- eg.png
|- blogs
  |- post.png
  |- whatever-anything.png

* supa :

DB:
{
  Desc: string,
  works: [
    "Zoey & the Spirit of Juniper": [desc: string, url: string (url_to_images)]
  ],
  blogs: [
    "heading-also-the-url-to-the-blog": string (html_page -> links_to_img_embedded)
  ]
}
